question.fine_print:
* This question will resolve based on the first data published by the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration for the whole year, including preliminary data and statistical projections. For example, the early estimates of traffic fatalities for 2023 were published in [this press release](https://www.nhtsa.gov/press-releases/2022-traffic-deaths-2023-early-estimates) on April 1, 2024, and the NHTSA estimate was 44,990.&#x20;
* Later revisions will not affect the resolution of this question.
* If the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration does not publish data for 2024 before January 1, 2026, this question will be **annulled**.

